56 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Your-paragraph-text-15.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eGraphic: Polygon | Source image: Bethesda Game Studios/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe second puzzle is a \u003cstrong\u003eblock puzzle in Vilverin Wendesel\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn the southern part of Vilverin Wendesel the dungeon, there is a puzzle with six blocks inside a room with six doors. Each block opens and closes a certain door in the room. Pressing the upper right block will open the door with the Vilverin chamber key (the key you need to proceed). Two of the other two blocks will open doors to rooms that contains chests, but be prepared to fight some undead.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere is a special switch you need to use to get a rare item called a \u003cstrong\u003evarla stone\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection tabindex=\"-1\" aria-label=\"carousel\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\":R4pdlhr96:\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\" data-pswp-height=\"720\" data-pswp-width=\"1280\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image of a Varla stone cage in Vilverin dungeon in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h36m45s141.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\" data-pswp-height=\"720\" data-pswp-width=\"1280\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image of a cube switch in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-11h37m27s728.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e1/2\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Bethesda Game Studios/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can get a varla Stone, a valuable item worth 1,000 gold, if you know the right switch to press. When in the far south room of Vilverin Wendesel, you will see a “Varla Stone Cage” hanging in the center. Defeat the undead and walk up the stairs that lead to the upper level of the room. There is a cube-shaped switch there. Press it and the cage containing the stone will lower and you can go collect it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"vilverin-dungeon-loot-in-oblivion-remastered\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eVilverin dungeon loot in Oblivion Remastered\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOther than the varla stone, this dungeon is a good opportunity to get some starter armor for your journey and other items like the \u003cstrong\u003eayeleid statue\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ewelkynd stones\u003c/strong\u003e. You can collect loads of welkynd stones as you explore the dungeon, they are the glowing blue stones that help light the building. Here is how to get everything else.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection tabindex=\"-1\" aria-label=\"carousel\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\":R61dlhr96:\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\" data-pswp-height=\"720\" data-pswp-width=\"1280\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image of iron boots sitting on a crate in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-10h21m36s820.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\" data-pswp-height=\"720\" data-pswp-width=\"1280\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A graphic showing a iron graeves on the ground in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 744px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e1/2\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Bethesda Game Studios/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eJust as you enter the dungeon, walk down the spiral staircase to the first room. Defeat the bandits so you’re safe and look around. Near the center of the room there is a crate with a chest and other items on top of it. The chest \u003cstrong\u003econtains 11 gold\u003c/strong\u003e. Here is what you can grab sitting on crate:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIron curiass\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIron boots\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIron claymore\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you look to the right of the cart, you’ll see some sleeping bags on the ground. You can also pick up a set of \u003cstrong\u003eiron greaves\u003c/strong\u003e that are sitting on the ground.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"720\" data-pswp-width=\"1280\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image of Ayleid Statue in a dungeon in Oblivion Remastered. It’s sitting on a center pedestal. \" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/vlcsnap-2025-04-24-12h32m16s245.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Bethesda Game Studios/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe other item you will want to grab is the\u003cstrong\u003e ayeleid statue\u003c/strong\u003e located in \u003cstrong\u003eSel Sancremathi\u003c/strong\u003e. It’s sitting right in the open but it’s easy to walk past if you aren’t looking for it. Just walk up to it to collect it. It’s worth 250 gold.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
